OL,6,FRemembering that day, he said: "You go
OL,7,Fback to the smells, the feeling the
OL,8,Fimages, that we all went through on
OL,9,Fthe day. Loved ones waiting at home to
OL,10,Fhear what happened to their family
OL,11,Fmembers... it brings it all back."
OL,13,FToday, an investigation has found
OL,14,F"fundamental failures" and "concerted
OL,15,Fefforts" to pin the blame on Liverpool
OL,16,Ffans during the Hillsborough disaster
OL,17,Fwould have resulted in gross
OL,18,Fmisconduct proceedings.
