OL,3,C'It can't happen again': Hillsborough
OL,4,Csurvivor speaks as new report released
OL,6,FA new report published by the
OL,7,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,8,F(IOPC) has found that 12 officers
OL,9,Fwould have faced misconduct
OL,10,Fproceedings under current laws.
OL,12,FHowever, the IOPC says that
OL,13,Fproceedings cannot be brought because
OL,14,Flegislation at the time of the
OL,15,Finvestigation prevented officers from
OL,16,Fbeing disciplined after they retire.
