OL,3,C'It can't happen again': Hillsborough
OL,4,Csurvivor speaks as new report released
OL,6,F97 Liverpool supporters died at the FA
OL,7,FCup semi-final on 15 April 1989 when
OL,8,Fpolice opened an exit gate to the
OL,9,Fground to alleviate crowding outside
OL,10,Fand failed to direct supporters away
OL,11,Ffrom the tunnel leading to the central
OL,12,Fpens where the crush happened.
OL,14,FReacting to today's report, Dean said:
OL,15,F"It's a stain on the system that we've
OL,16,Flived in that for all these years, new
OL,17,Ffacts still come out to this day.
