OL,3,C'It can't happen again': Hillsborough
OL,4,Csurvivor speaks as new report released
OL,6,F"Seeing reports like this, reading the
OL,7,Fdetail, and thinking of the people
OL,8,Fthat we've lost along the way...
OL,9,FThere's been no accountability, and
OL,10,Fit's very hard to swallow."
OL,12,FHe says the impact of the disaster
OL,13,Fcontinues to affect him, and other
OL,14,Fsurvivors to this day.
OL,16,F"It continues to define us as people,"
OL,17,Fhe said. "You can't escape it. It's
OL,18,Fbeen life for almost four decades."
