OL,3,C'It can't happen again': Hillsborough
OL,4,Csurvivor speaks as new report released
OL,6,FHe says the latest report "just adds
OL,7,Fweight to the case for a Hillsborough
OL,8,Flaw", which would force public
OL,9,Fofficials and contractors to tell the
OL,10,Ftruth in the aftermath of disasters.
OL,12,F"I think Hillsborough will be classed
OL,13,Fas the biggest injustice that this
OL,14,Fcountry has ever seen," he added.
OL,16,F"How can it be that 36 years after a
OL,17,Ftragedy, that we still have reports
OL,18,Fcoming out highlighting the failures
OL,19,Fof the police service?
