OL,3,C'It can't happen again': Hillsborough
OL,4,Csurvivor speaks as new report released
OL,6,F"That can't be right, it isn't right -
OL,7,Fnot when you have 97 victims who
OL,8,Funfortunately have not got justice and
OL,9,Faccountability for what happened on
OL,10,Fthat day.
OL,12,F"It can't happen again."
OL,14,FResponding to the Independent Office
OL,15,Ffor Police Conduct (IOPC) report, Home
OL,16,FSecretary Shabana Mahmood paid tribute
OL,17,Fto the survivors and families of those
OL,18,Fkilled in Hillsborough disaster.
