OL,3,C'It can't happen again': Hillsborough
OL,4,Csurvivor speaks as new report released
OL,6,FShe added: "They have faced years of
OL,7,Fmistreatment and delay, but thanks to
OL,8,Ftheir tireless campaigning we are
OL,9,Fintroducing the Hillsborough Law which
OL,10,Fwill place a legal duty of candour on
OL,11,Fpublic servants and authorities.
OL,13,F"There is also now legislation in
OL,14,Fplace which means that police officers
OL,15,Fcannot evade misconduct proceedings by
OL,16,Fretiring or resigning, so these
OL,17,Ffailings can never be repeated."
